  <brief_title>Cognitive Behavioral Therapy for Core Autism Symptoms in School-Aged Children: A Randomized, Controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>BIACA-2</acronym>
  <official_title>Cognitive Behavioral Therapy for Core Autism Symptoms in School-Aged Children: A Randomized, Controlled Trial</official_title>
