  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to examine the efficacy of a cognitive behavioral therapy (CBT)
      program for treating core autism symptoms, social and emotional problems, and adaptive
      behavior deficits in children with autism spectrum disorders.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
